reviewText: I like Wade Bowen and his music, particularly his up-tempo rockers. Live at Billy Bobs Texas finds Bowen doing mostly hits, however. These are crowd pleasers mostly with a few rockers thrown in. I think the ladies will really like this performance. For me, while it's good and covers the Wade Bowen hit catalog, check out Live at the Ble Light album to get the true Red Dirt Country Bowen is capable of.
